text: The Dutch Low Saxon Wikipedia is the Dutch Low Saxon-language edition of Wikipedia. This edition was started in 24 March 2006. As of 23 August 2015, it has over 5,748 articles.List of Wikipedias on Meta-Wiki. ==References== ==Other websites== *Dutch Low Saxon Wikipedia main page Category:Wikipedias Category:Websites established in 2006
